		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Good [4.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Sarker&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Through my efforts of levelling ranger &amp; ninja, I have often found myself hard-up for cash, and have tried all of these different options.<br /><br />My opinion on the matter:  Invest in crafting.<br /><br />As a ranger58/thief29, I can efficiently farm 15-25K per hour on elementals, couerls, cockatrices, rams, or silks... i always liked to switch it up to avoid boredom.<br /><br />In some of the less mined areas (Ifrit's Cauldron for mining, Attowah Chasm for excavation, Lufaise Meadows for logging), I was able to increase this to about $40k per hour, so I pretty much dropped farming.<br /><br />Now, I have taken a considerable portion of that money and invested it into crafts (woodworking &amp; alchemy for me, but any will do provided you get it past 60).  With the recent extreme increases in mid-level crafting materials, I can sit around and HQ some basic materials for anywhere between 80-100K per hour.  For a 50/50 chance at HQ'ing, you need to be about 50 points above the skillcap, and preferably craft on darksday and/or newmoon.<br /><br />Now, whenever I get low on cash, I combine the 2nd and 3rd options, I head to Lufaise Meadows with a couple stacks of hatchets, wind crystals &amp; bundling twine, and typically come back with ~50K in logs (oak &amp; elm), and ~100K in lumber (Ash &amp; Arrowwood) in about 2 hours.<br /><br />Hope this helps.  I don't mind sharing, because there is literally a never-ending demand for these materials.<br /><br />Good luck, and feel free to /tell if you need info on farming / logging locations, or crafting ideas.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Sarker of Bastok on Remora Server<br /><B>RNG58</b>, NIN32, THF33, RDM30, BLM15, WAR18, BST09 (lol)<br />Woodworking 62, Alchemy 25, Bonecraft 9, Gold 10</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
